RT-Sample-YAPC2010 version 0.01

This is simply a collection of sample code discussed during my presentation
at YAPC::NA 2010 in Columbus OH
http://yapc2010.com/yn2010/talk/2648

How to install:

1. perl Makefile.PL
2. make
3. make install (may need root permissions)
4. Edit your /opt/rt3/etc/RT_SiteConfig.pm 
    Set(@Plugins, qw(RT::Sample::YAPC2010));
    or add <RT::Sample::YAPC2010> to your existing @Plugins line
5. Clear your mason cache
     rm -rf /opt/rt3/var/mason_data/obj
6. Restart your webserver

